org.apache.commons.math4.util

Class CombinatoricsUtils.FactorialLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.math4.util.CombinatoricsUtils.FactorialLog
  • Enclosing class:
    CombinatoricsUtils

    public static final class CombinatoricsUtils.FactorialLog
extends Object
    Class for computing the natural logarithm of the factorial of n. It allows to allocate a cache of precomputed values. In case of cache miss, computation is preformed by a call to Gamma.logGamma(double).
